OL,5, Bryan Adams has spoken for the first   
OL,6, time about how his friendship with     
OL,7, Princess Diana was sparked by a song he
OL,8, wrote about her doomed marriage.       
OL,10,FThe singer recalled how the late royal 
OL,11,Fsaid she found the lyrics about him    
OL,12,F"losing his mind" on the day she       
OL,13,Fmarried Prince Charles "very funny".   
OL,15,FSpeaking to the Sunday Times, Adams    
OL,16,Fadded that Diana invited him round for 
OL,17,Ftea so she could hear the song again.  
OL,19,FHe retired the song when she died in   
OL,20,F1997 "out of respect", he added.       
